Package ohos.sensor.bean

Class CategoryOther

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.sensor.bean.SensorBase
      • ohos.sensor.bean.CategoryOther

  • public final class CategoryOther
extends SensorBase
    Inherits from SensorBase and describes sensors in the other category (a category other than motion, environment, orientation, and light) on hardware devices.

    This class describes the sensor types in the other category, such as the Hall effect, magnet bracket, and pressure detection sensors. It also provides the method for constructing a CategoryOther instance.

    Since:
    1

        name - Indicates the name of the sensor.
        vendor - Indicates the manufacturer of the sensor.
        version - Indicates the version of the sensor.
        upperRange - Indicates the maximum measurement range of the sensor.
        resolution - Indicates the resolution of the sensor.
        flags - Indicates the flags of the sensor.
        cacheMaxCount - Indicates the maximum number of hardware FIFO elements supported by the sensor.
